                                        Adding of signatures

  1.  Go to the system->templates folder in the front end of papertrail.

  2.  Edit/Check-out the template.html file.

  3.  Use this html editor to the make the changes/Create:http://htmledit.squarefree.com/

  4.  Once completed. Check-in the file and send email to confirm the signature.

  5.  UPGRADE: always keep the html in a checked out position to prevent from resetting the template.
